<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.1.1">
<l>uyarvaṟa vuyarnala muṭaiyavaṉ yavaṉavaṉ</l>
<l>mayarvaṟa matinala maruḷiṉaṉ yavaṉava</l>
<l>ṉayarvaṟu mamararka ḷatipati yavaṉavaṉ</l>
<l>ṟuyaraṟu cuṭaraṭi toḻuteḻeṉ maṉaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who is he who possesses heigh goodness without haughtiness,</l>
<l>who is he who graces minds with goodness so that confusion is severed,</l>
<l>who is he who is the overlord of the immortals in whom tiredness is severed?</l>
<l>Rise in worship to [his] glowing feet by which misery is severed, my mind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
